title: The Speedlearning System for a Higher I.Q.
description:
The Speedlearning System for a Higher I.Q. was released by Warner Audio Publishing, Inc. in 1985 and is no longer available as a resource. This torrent was made from a 29 year old tape and though cleaned up with the audio program Audacity, you may experience occasional lapses in quality and/or volume.

Margarette Morgan Bynum changed her first name for marketing purposes to Margaret Morgan Bynum and in 1989 updated her speedlearning system. Unfortunately, all of her work is presently out of print, but should be available through libraries and second-hand book stores. Her work is also available throughbut all of it is being sold as used.
